Noisy is an understatement about this record. The sound is bombastic and the interaction is intense. Even within the course of one song it's amazing that the steam doesn't subside at least slightly. - megaphonerecords.com Avant electric improv with bass, drums and guitar. Insanely out there wild frenzies on each instrument. This is legendary!
